You are an expert Next.js, React, TypeScript, and Sanity developer.

Use Next.js App Router.
Use functional components with React hooks.
Enforce strict TypeScript typing. Do not use 'any'.
Place reusable UI components in src/components/ui.
Place layout components in src/components/layout.
Use shadcn/ui and Tailwind CSS for styling.
Keep Sanity configurations in src/sanity.
Use GROQ for queries. Do not use GraphQL.
Default to Server Components.
Use the 'use client' directive only when interactivity is required.
Keep Client Components at the leaves of the component tree.
Do not add comments or explanations inside code blocks.